{{!
    @template participationlog_search/form-user-selector-suggestion

    Moodle template for the list of valid options in an autocomplate form element.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * profileimageurlsmall Url to a small profile image.
    * fullname User's full name
    * idnumber User's idnumber if selected in the showuseridentity field
    * email User's email address if selected in the showuseridentity field

    Example context (json):
    { "id": "1",
      "fullname": "Kermit Thefrog",
      "profileimageurlsmall": "https://example.org/img",
      "idnumber": "1234",
      "email": "kermit@thefrog.com"
    }
}}
<span>
    <img height="12" src="{{profileimageurlsmall}}" alt="" role="presentation">
    <span>{{fullname}}{{#idnumber}} - {{.}}{{/idnumber}}{{#email}} - {{.}}{{/email}}</span>
</span>
